title: 12 Guitar Duets of Mikis Theodorakis
description:
Artists: Notis Mavroudis (guitar) & Panagiotis Margaris (guitar)


Translation:

xartaetoi -> kites

o kipos empaine sti thalassa -> the garden was entering the sea

tin porta anoigo to vrady -> i open the door at night

an thimitheis to oneiro -> if you will remember the dream

to traino fevgei stis okto -> the train leaves at 8 o'clock

serpico -> this is the theme from the movie "serpico"

to gelasto paidi -> the smiling boy (it is written for Lambrakis who was assassinated by the palace - search the movie "Z" by Costa Gavras)

ligo akoma -> just yet ( a little more)

omorfi poli -> beautiful city

nikta magikia -> magic night (enchanted night)

tou mikrou voria -> the small northern wind

dakrismena matia -> tearful eyes
